icket\u201d instances.<\/em><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-2eb84a5 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"2eb84a5\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-4e1dded\" data-id=\"4e1dded\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-40dbc24 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"40dbc24\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1000\" height=\"750\" src=\"https:\/\/micepad.co\/tw\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/5\/2019\/04\/alexander-londono-319305-unsplash-1024x767-1.jpeg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-2295\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/micepad.co\/tw\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/5\/2019\/04\/alexander-londono-319305-unsplash-1024x767-1.jpeg 1023w, https:\/\/micepad.co\/tw\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/5\/2019\/04\/alexander-londono-319305-unsplash-1024x767-1-300x225.jpeg 300w, https:\/\/micepad.co\/tw\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/5\/2019\/04\/alexander-londono-319305-unsplash-1024x767-1-768x576.jpeg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" title=\"\">\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ac95e94 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"ac95e94\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"tve-droppable\">2. Promote sponsors<\/h3>\n<p class=\"tve-droppable\">Advertising and marketing the event is costly. Being able to promote sponsors through push notifications in-app is a valuable way to generate revenue before the event even starts. Sell ad-space on banners, customise information pages and promote individual speakers through a medium you\u00a0<em>know\u00a0<\/em>your guests will access.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-254ac72 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"254ac72\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-2e146a3\" data-id=\"2e146a3\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-a38d015 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"a38d015\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1000\" height=\"667\" src=\"https:\/\/micepad.co\/tw\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/5\/2019\/04\/mathieu-turle-524977-unsplash-1024x683-1.jpeg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-2294\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/micepad.co\/tw\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/5\/2019\/04\/mathieu-turle-524977-unsplash-1024x683-1.jpeg 1024w, https:\/\/micepad.co\/tw\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/5\/2019\/04\/mathieu-turle-524977-unsplash-1024x683-1-300x200.jpeg 300w, https:\/\/micepad.co\/tw\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/5\/2019\/04\/mathieu-turle-524977-unsplash-1024x683-1-768x512.jpeg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" title=\"\">\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-6c510bc elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"6c510bc\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"tve-droppable\">3. Overheads<\/h3>\n<p class=\"tve-droppable\">Overheads stand for \u2018any indirect costs that are still related to the event\u2019. This includes \u2018auxiliary support tech\u2019 like what QuickMobile mentioned, which could be anything from WhatsApp to a Customer-Relationship Management system (CRM) to answer enquiries and other customer needs.<\/p>\n<p class=\"tve-droppable\">While it is true that you could coordinate your event through a judicious use of email, Excel, WhatsApp chat groups, landing pages and social media, it is\u00a0<strong>very easy to lose track of so many platforms.<\/strong><\/p>\n<p class=\"tve-droppable\">With an event app, you can have a bird\u2019s eye view of all your running programs &#8211; especially useful with multiple events. Not only do you get rid of the possibility of (horror of horrors)\u00a0<em>losing track of what you\u2019ve sent out,\u00a0<\/em>you also save yourself the time needed to create and update\u00a0<em>every single platform<\/em>.<\/p>\n<p class=\"tve-droppable\">Even better: most event apps have also grown to include emailing capabilities, allowing you to upload guest lists and send out RSVP requests, confirmations and even full marketing campaigns without needing an email platform.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-0f61794 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"0f61794\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-60af0e4\" data-id=\"60af0e4\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-c09d115 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"c09d115\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1000\" height=\"802\" src=\"https:\/\/micepad.co\/tw\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/5\/2019\/04\/lucas-favre-667552-unsplash-1024x821-1.jpeg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-2293\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/micepad.co\/tw\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/5\/2019\/04\/lucas-favre-667552-unsplash-1024x821-1.jpeg 1024w, https:\/\/micepad.co\/tw\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/5\/2019\/04\/lucas-favre-667552-unsplash-1024x821-1-300x241.jpeg 300w, https:\/\/micepad.co\/tw\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/5\/2019\/04\/lucas-favre-667552-unsplash-1024x821-1-768x616.jpeg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" title=\"\">\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-a4aae20 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"a4aae20\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"tve-droppable\">4. Hardware<\/h3>\n<p class=\"tve-droppable\">Many events often have a Q&amp;A portion. Typically, attendees will go up to a mic stand to ask speakers their question. However, with an event app, not only can you do away with the mic stand (and wait time for the guest to make their way down), you can also moderate the questions asked.<\/p>\n<p class=\"tve-droppable\">On top of that, it\u2019s been proven that anonymity will increase the number of questions asked.<\/p>\n<p class=\"tve-droppable\">Here\u2019s some other hardware you can save on:<\/p>\n<ul class=\"tve-droppable\">\n<li>\n<p>Schedule displays<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<p>Printers (not just papers!)<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<p>Cameras and cameramen (Leave it to the guests)<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-d8ff028 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"d8ff028\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-08efcc4\" data-id=\"08efcc4\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-fd54b25 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"fd54b25\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1000\" height=\"662\" src=\"https:\/\/micepad.co\/tw\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/5\/2019\/04\/aneta-pawlik-651610-unsplash-1024x678-1.jpeg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-2296\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/micepad.co\/tw\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/5\/2019\/04\/aneta-pawlik-651610-unsplash-1024x678-1.jpeg 1024w, https:\/\/micepad.co\/tw\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/5\/2019\/04\/aneta-pawlik-651610-unsplash-1024x678-1-300x199.jpeg 300w, https:\/\/micepad.co\/tw\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/5\/2019\/04\/aneta-pawlik-651610-unsplash-1024x678-1-768x509.jpeg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" title=\"\">\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-9083b8c elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"9083b8c\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"tve-droppable\">5. Venue &amp; Catering<\/h3>\n<p class=\"tve-droppable\">Knowing how many people are actually attending can save you quite a bit in terms of venue and catering. One creative way of using the event app is by conducting a live poll at the start of the event to confirm numbers and determine any special dietary requirements.<\/p>\n<p class=\"tve-droppable\">Confirming the check-in numbers as the guests arrive is also a good way to know whether you need to open that side room to the main auditorium. (And whether or not you have a high check-in to RSVP rate)<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>1. Printing As\u00a0previously mentioned, you can eliminate all printing costs for your event by uploading your content and material onto your app. [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":2573,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[131,133],"tags":[110,120,136],"class_list":["post-2290","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-how-to-tutorials","category-industry-insights","tag-event-apps","tag-event-management","tag-good-to-know"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/micepad.co\/tw\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2290","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/